<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一年一下子就過去了耶！<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年雖然發生了許多事，<delay20 />
卻為我帶來<delay8 />很多開心的回憶喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了讓明年的自己<delay8 />能更加強而有力，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會拿出幹勁好好努力的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚跨年倒數的時候，<delay20 />
好像會放煙火耶！<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跨年的活動<delay8 />真是熱鬧呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也一定<delay8 />會參加吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />參加這種活動<delay8 />就是要熱鬧才開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們就使出全力來慶祝新年吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要想到新的一年<delay8 />馬上就要開始了，<delay20 />
我就覺得<delay8 />莫名興奮起來啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也算是幫<tag a="90" b="27" />年做個結尾，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就讓我們一起<delay8 />
把氣氛炒熱到最高點吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼年末的最後一天<delay8 />
會讓人這麼靜不下心啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不管再怎麼猜，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不知道明年<delay8 />會是怎麼樣的一年，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我預想明年<delay8 />一定會過得很開心喔！</message>
</msbt>